text: Federico Barocci, born Federico Fiori (born 1535 or 1536 in Urbino, died 1612) was an important Italian painter. He is also known as Fiori da Urbino. His real name was Federico Fiori. His style is between that of Mannerism and Baroque. ==Related pages== * List of Italian painters Category:1530s births Category:1612 deaths Category:16th-century Italian painters Category:17th- century Italian painters
